Package: splithalfr
Title: Extensible Bootstrapped Split-half Reliabilities
Version: 1.0.1
Author: Thomas Pronk
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Pronk", email = "pronkthomas@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates scores and bootstrapped split-half reliabilities for reaction time tasks and questionnaires. 
	The splithalfr can be extended by custom scoring methods for user-provided datasets.
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
